pageContext.claim: “A Rigged System - They don’t want to turn over Documents to Congress. What are they afraid of? Why so much redacting? Why such unequal 'justice?' At some point I will have no choice but to use the powers granted to the Presidency and get involved!”
pageContext.analysis: The Department of Justice has turned over thousands of documents to Congress about the FBI's decision making in matters involving the 2016 election.
